Package io.knowledgelinks.cicd.semantic.versioning.api

Class SemanticVersioningApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.knowledgelinks.cicd.semantic.versioning.api.SemanticVersioningApi
  • public class SemanticVersioningApi
extends Object
    The main class used to manage the application. Contains methods to retrieve all pertinent application data. The class needs to be instantiated using the SemanticVersioningApiBuilder class.
    Author:
    mstabile75
